            <h1 class="signature" translate="no">getFont(This :: <a href="#t:wxTextAttr/0">wxTextAttr</a>())<span class="signature-arrow">&nbsp;-&gt;&nbsp;</span><span class="signature-result"><a href="wxFont.html#t:wxFont/0">wxFont:wxFont</a>()</span></h1>




          <a href="https://github.com/erlang/otp/blob/master/lib/wx/src/gen/wxTextAttr.erl#L158" class="icon-action" rel="help nofollow" aria-label="View Source">
            <i class="ri-code-s-slash-line" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          </a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="docstring">



<p>Creates and returns a font specified by the font attributes in the <a href="wxTextAttr.html"><code class="inline">wxTextAttr</code></a> object.</p><p>Note that <a href="wxTextAttr.html"><code class="inline">wxTextAttr</code></a> does not store a <a href="wxFont.html"><code class="inline">wxFont</code></a> object, so this is only a temporary font.</p><p>For greater efficiency, access the font attributes directly.</p>
  </section>
</section>
